import React from 'react'

function AddTodo() {
    return (
        <form style={{ display: 'flex' }}>
            <input
                type='text'
                name="title"
                style={{ felx: '10', padding: '5px' }}
                placeholder="Add Todo..." />
            <input
                type="submit"
                value="Submit"
                className="btn"
                style={{ flex: '1' }} />

        </form>
    )
}

export default AddTodo
